    v2 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.07 * v0 + 0.79)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.06)) * 0.02)
    v1 = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.52 + tmp + 0.87) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.93)))
    v0 = 1.00
    v2 = 0.35
    v0 = (0.90 - v0)
    v2 = (0.40 * wp.exp((v2 + 0.33 - v2 + 0.42)))
